magicbook.gtlitecore.api.utils.stream

接口 Gatherer.Downstream<T>

  • 类型参数:
    T - The type of elements this downstream accepts.
    封闭接口:
    Gatherer<T,A,R>
    函数接口:
    这是一个函数接口, 因此可用作 lambda 表达式或方法引用的赋值目标。

    @FunctionalInterface
public static interface Gatherer.Downstream<T>
    A downstream object is the next stage in a pipeline of operations, to which elements can be sent.

    • 方法概要

      所有方法 实例方法 抽象方法 默认方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      default boolean isRejecting()
      Checks whether the next stage is known to not want any more elements sent to it.
      boolean push(T element)
      Pushes, if possible, the provided element downstream -- to the next stage in the pipeline.

    • 方法详细资料

      • push

        boolean push(T element)
        Pushes, if possible, the provided element downstream -- to the next stage in the pipeline.
        参数:
        element - The element to push downstream
        返回:
        Returns true if more elements can be sent, and false if not.

      • isRejecting

        default boolean isRejecting()
        Checks whether the next stage is known to not want any more elements sent to it.
        返回:
        Returns true if this downstream is known not to want anymore elements sent to it, false if otherwise.
